<p><strong>Q3 — Optimization:</strong> Double down on tactics that worked. Cut tactics that underperformed. Refine your approach.</p>
<p><strong>Q4 — Push:</strong> Maximize opportunities before year-end. Plan next year's budget based on data.</p>
