<p><strong>Google Analytics 4:</strong> Track referral traffic from new domains. A backlink that drives zero visitors has limited value.</p>
<p><strong>Ahrefs Webmaster Tools:</strong> Verify your site for free access to full backlink data, including new and lost links, anchor text, and referring domain quality.</p>
<p><strong>Manual Spreadsheet:</strong> Track every outreach email, response, and link placement. This manual CRM costs nothing and teaches you what works.</p>
